com.b2international.snowowl.snomed.snomedrefset

Interface SnomedAttributeValueRefSetMember

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.cdo.CDOObject, org.eclipse.emf.cdo.common.id.CDOWithID, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SnomedRefSetMember
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Rf2RefSetMember, SnomedAttributeValueRefSetMemberImpl, UnsupportedRf2RefSetMember

    public interface SnomedAttributeValueRefSetMember
extends SnomedRefSetMember
    Represents a SNOMED CT attribute value reference set member. The purpose of this reference set member is to allow a value from a given range to be associated with a SNOMED CT component.

    The following features are supported:

    • Value Id

    See Also:
    SnomedRefSetPackage.getSnomedAttributeValueRefSetMember()
